{"tid":1564233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我並唔認為雨傘運動係失敗","createTime":"2019-09-12T16:28:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T06:29:44.000Z","uid":98915,"like":123,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"4e149dd6c1ee3756d1503d586fcbcfda37fbc887","tid":1564233,"uid":98915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:28:57.000Z","msg":"冇雨傘運動 根本冇今日返送中運動嘅團結<br />\n點解要攞雨傘運動嘅所有嘢指責<br />\n<br />\n雨傘冇成果嘅最大原因並唔係因為嘉年華<br />\n而係因為我哋唔團結 訴求亦都太多<br />\n我哋根本係之後好多人都冇再出嚟幫手<br />\n亦都好多人互相指責<br />\n<br />\n但係雨傘運動令我哋成長 令我哋學習<br />\n成為一個好好嘅啟蒙運動<br />\n當年我地亦都做咗一個好好嘅榜樣<br />\n比而家嘅後生聽 運動嘅重點係要做啲咩<br />\n<br />\n請大家喺個憤怒中醒一醒<br />\n毋忘運動初心"},{"pid":"8d3261f5fd10453dd9300553a650e3f8a7c0fc1d","tid":1564233,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:30:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"bb5c26cd9a4ccc3df1d7f1e0956165b8a4a375a7","tid":1564233,"uid":98915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:33:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3761cc3e6510951e289eb10629631e0a85e4dddb","tid":1564233,"uid":98915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:35:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" cl