:0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:17:10.000Z","msg":"Carnival 同carnival 加勇武 分別<br />\n已經唔同"},{"pid":"6e8e4c1b69c484ae55917b051cb9e3a08ab27678","tid":1564233,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:18:28.000Z","msg":"咪撚玩啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9ddfc5bf073826a849ca36ff6a2d053606f1985","tid":1564233,"uid":168250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:19:25.000Z","msg":"傘運催化左本土派嘅進程，令本土主義崛起，當年青政係因為佢地對大台，對飯民好失望而組隊選區議會立法會<br />\n本民前嘅創始成員更加係反對傳統大台，主張以武制暴，所以先組織政黨，最後天琦仲係新東攞六萬幾票（好掛住你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），你再睇吓當日天琦講嘅八字真言而家全部人都識<br />\n雨傘運動本質上失敗，但係佢嘅影響一路都係到"},{"pid":"5b63bc0a90613d46ab7e3c6f9a9f48317acc4494","tid":1564233,"uid":98915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93b59cf97d6cd2ea0af66373fad75c0c286ecb4a","tid":1564233,"uid":201031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:14:00.000Z","msg":"阿Q精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:22:10.000Z","msg":"唔係咁講㗎 啟蒙運動呢個概念係歷史上不嬲都有<br />\n<br />\n清朝公車上車 之後五四 六四 呢啲大型運動<br />\n有邊一次唔係失敗吖<br />\n但係佢地真係造就左學生救國嘅風氣<br />\n同埋民眾運動嘅凝聚力"},{"pid":"4eb01e101d8397a104c2daed552c243b2ed31dfb","tid":1564233,"uid":185762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:23:36.000Z","msg":"失敗又點 我地最終目標唔係一兩次城功咁簡單"},{"pid":"a9d6c3149f346cb44c5d0e1ce9bcbd2f91e19516","tid":1564233,"uid":98915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"108d878330d656f4b23244c366417d81659af8cf","tid":1564233,"uid":15224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:16:11.000Z","msg":"我永遠唔會忘記隔離龍和道打到仆街, 我一個人係夏愨道大嗌叫人過去幫手, 班金鐘人仲&quot;係咩碰&quot;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:25:21.000Z","msg":"辛苦你了巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明白嘅 當初香港人對暴力有潔癖<br />\n今時今日唔會再咁 因為我哋學精咗"},{"pid":"a6e6c29015a2a633fba63c71bebaa1ba03348ffd","tid":1564233,"uid":294275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:26:03.000Z","msg":"有同感，雨傘其實啟蒙左好多人。<br />\n亦將爭取自由嘅種子播開左"},{"pid":"f2bb90b640bbe822cdd2dd630397406d3fa67193","tid":1564233,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:26:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3e3e8214f046f9e313bfd044b38e3a08ef33e9fe","tid":1564233,"uid":257190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84472edb104097f384f15090c64211e07f3625bf","tid":1564233,"uid":25468,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:46:10.000Z","msg":"雨革失敗最大原因係勇武同和理非各自為戰，和理非大台化被騎劫，根本完全唔撚關唱歌事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:30:34.000Z","msg":"唱歌係冇問題，如果可以唱埋美國國歌，就更好<br />\n唱願榮光歸香港同美國國唱係可以同時進行<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以睇下呢個post呀手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1563787/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1563787/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n雨傘同魚蛋教識我地唔可以分化，割蓆，同篤灰<br />\n前人流過嘅血同淚，留比我地呢個大原則<br />\n兄弟爬山，希望所有人都記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}